targets.query: SELECT top("Load", 3) FROM "perftest" WHERE ("trial" = 'mcdawsdirectubuntu' OR "instance_type" = 'ProLiant_m710x_Server_Cartridge') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval * 10), "VGA", "instance_type", "test_type" fill(null)

SELECT max("stddev") FROM (SELECT stddev("Load")/mean("Load") as "stddev" FROM "perftest" WHERE (("instance_type" = 'g2.2xlarge' AND "time" > '2021-02-13 06:00:00') OR "instance_type" != 'g2.2xlarge') AND $timeFilter AND "seq" <> '0' GROUP BY time(30m), "VGA", "instance_type", "test" fill(linear)) WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(30m), "VGA", "instance_type" fill(linear)

SELECT mean("stddev"), max("stddev"), sum("count") as "count" FROM (SELECT stddev("Load")/mean("Load") as "stddev", count("Load") FROM "perftest" WHERE (("instance_type" = 'g2.2xlarge' AND "time" > '2021-02-13 06:00:00') OR "instance_type" != 'g2.2xlarge') AND $timeFilter AND "seq" <> '0' GROUP BY "VGA", "instance_type", "test", "os_version" fill(null)) WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY "VGA", "instance_type", "os_version" fill(linear)

SELECT stddev("Load") /mean("Load") as "stddev", count("Load") FROM "perftest" WHERE ("instance_id" =~ /^$instanceId$/ AND "test" =~ /^$test$/ AND "instance_type" =~ /^$instanceType$/ AND "seq" <> '0') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "test", "VGA", "instance_type", "opengl_dev" fill(null)

SELECT stddev("Load") /mean("Load") as "stddev", min("Load"), max("Load") FROM "perftest" WHERE ("instance_id" =~ /^$instanceId$/ AND "test" =~ /^$test$/ AND "instance_type" =~ /^$instanceType$/ AND "seq" <> '0') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1d), "instance_type" fill(null)
